{"tid":1632020,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"連登仔竟然搞唔掂經濟通投票?","createTime":"2019-10-06T16:48:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T16:55:16.000Z","uid":198974,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"369fde872735cca54f4d7c0d9f754ae45478993e","tid":1632020,"uid":198974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:48:24.000Z","msg":"形勢不妙 (51% 藍 vs 49% 黃)，可能很多大陸五毛投票， 雖然 TG《美國白宮聯署鍵盤戰士》已作出呼籲，但可能人數上始終鬥不過。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n---<br />\n建制陣營無視警員違反《警察條例》，不展示委任證和警員編號，卻極力推動禁止示威者蒙面的《蒙面法》。<br />\n<br />\n請各位鍵盤戰士進入以下 Link 勇武作戰，要徹底擊敗建制派！<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.etnet.com.hk/mobile/tc/lifestyle/voting.php?id=1228\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.etnet.com.hk%2Fmobile%2Ftc%2Flifestyle%2Fvoting.php%3Fid%3D1228&d=QZYHYFPECKJw76TN47EEpuNdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=d5535276\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.etnet.com.hk/mobile/tc/lifestyle/voting.php?id=1228</a><br />\n<br />\n1. 你認為香港應否就《反蒙面法》立法？<br />\n投「不應該」<br />\n<br />\n2. 你認為立《反蒙面法》能否減少暴力衝突？<br />\n投「不能」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a34c91f6b63d1d5e29e9839e6d2bd6e22ee912b","tid":1632020,"uid":198974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:48:44.000Z","msg":"自推 1/20"},{"pid":"6d85a1ca7077b3508f1ce56aad23821a8cafbe6d","tid":1632020,"uid":198974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:48:55.000Z","msg":"自推 2/20"},{"pid":"b092d651bad91a2c272c9f9cfdd2b365fc7333f6","tid":1632020,"uid":198974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:49:07.000Z","msg":"自推 3/20